Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.87,0:22:15.48,OPED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}任何人都还未发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.66,0:22:17.61,OPED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(50,50)}未知の大陸に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.66,0:22:17.61,OPED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}未知的大陆
